---
import type { GetStaticPaths } from "astro";
export const getStaticPaths = (() => {
	return [{ params: { author: "Pedro", title: "Harry Potter" } }, { params: { author: "Luis", title: "Harry Potter 2" } }, { params: { author: "Maria", title: "Harry Potter 3" } }];
}) satisfies GetStaticPaths;

const { author, title } = Astro.params;
---

<h1>Book: {title}</h1>

<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Debitis quas dicta repudiandae quaerat earum ipsa eaque natus provident temporibus est doloribus, voluptate sit suscipit incidunt accusantium exercitationem illum odit enim?</p>

<p>Author: {author}</p>
